			<tr><td valign="top" width="75%"><span class="clsSmall">[LORE] [MAGIC] [NO DROP] </span><br><br><b>Skill:</b>&nbsp;Brass
&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>-1% to songs</i>
<br><b>Description:</b>&nbsp;Reduces the effectiveness of songs by 1-5%
<br><b>Drop Location:</b><br>Drops in Ocean of Tears off Quag Mealstrom. Used in the Singing Short Sword Quest.
<br><b>Rarity:</b>&nbsp;Rare
<br><b>Level to Attain:</b>&nbsp;40<br><br><img src="/images/stats/imgStatsAlluringHorn.jpg" hspace="10" vspace="10"><br><br><b>How to Obtain this Item</b><br>This item is needed to complete the Bard epic quest.<br><br>
The alluring horn drops off Quag Maelstrom, a named seafury cyclops that can be found in the Ocean of Tears. Quag is a tough seafury cyclops, and is around level 41-46, and hits for 60-120hp. He has the ability to drain mana when he hits you.<br><br>Turn the Alluring Horn into Fopar Fizfla in Steamfont (loc 120, -600) and he gives you a note and tells you about the mystical lute he wants to make.<br><br>&nbsp;<a href="/items.asp">Back to Items</a><br><br></td><td valign="top"><img src="/images/icons/imgIconhorn.jpg" align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10"><br clear="right"><br><span class="clsSmall"><b>Slot:</b><br>SECONDARY</span><br><span class="clsSmall"><b>Weight:</b>&nbsp;1.0</span>
